236,Orsay,,2026-02-22,,"Esplanade Valéry Giscard d""Estaing",Paris,,,,,,,,,,,"Have you ever seen the ballroom in the Musée d’Orsay? 🤩🥰 📍 Musée d’Orsay, Paris 💡 It’s well signposted but somehow everyone misses it: as you get out of the exhibitions hall, go towards the restaurant and follow the “Salle des Fêtes” sign until you reach the end of the corridor ✨ #museedorsay #paris #orsay #orsaymuseum #salledesfetes #ballroom #parismuseum  #parisfrance #parisienne #parismonamour #parisvibes #parismood #parisjetaime #parisianvibes #iloveparis #parisianlife #gersparis #damestravel #dametraveler #wearetravelgirls #sheisnotlost #shetravels #femmetravel #explorerbabes #worldofwanderlust #beautifuldestinations #luxuryworldtraveler #thetravelwomen",,,,,,0,,,,75007,Île-de-France,,True,True,16.0,11.0,,,,,,16.0€ / 11.0€ réduit,,,,,10000000,,,,,,https://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr,116,,,1,"As-tu déjà vu la salle de bal du Musée d’Orsay ? 🤩🥰 📍 Musée d’Orsay, Paris 💡 C’est bien indiqué mais tout le monde la rate : en sortant de la salle des expositions, dirige-toi vers le restaurant et suis le panneau “Salle des Fêtes” jusqu’au bout du couloir ✨ #museedorsay #paris #salledesfetes #museeparis #parisfrance #parisjetaime #parismonamour #vibesparisiennes #explorationparis #beautifuldestinations",,,https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=481f0124cb8ccb74&rlz=1C1GCEA_frFR1162FR1162&hl=fr-FR&sxsrf=AE3TifNtH8zUcXLl8y2OPy-8nkpOFtnfSg:1756159045770&uds=AOm0WdE2fekQnsyfYEw8JPYozOKzOKZWT8NLWBEtiDKaJmJEPRhAE7zqTc225YVvQ8FQ7b_Ud1OcON7_fbM34i7sB71cnTM-709VrP3mjp70oxuPrBgjk89ysu5YXl0OcZFebfBhymZWixigfLH-WNNzPu916oyPRA&q=Mus%C3%A9e+d%27Orsay+Avis&si=AMgyJEuedXoQ7ICPADCXSyTriyr2ffUHXzcmE_m54-7C4V-47ye3GpUFkttsE_8fEVFL0lCH9RGab8GTFOsQSyaXOxwTvq9KIWY_b07OwCW33XuNb4ylAsjWPE1se_8Lu78fmjnb1GVY&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwidmN6g-qaPAxV5KvsDHa2tETYQ_4MLegQIPxAP&biw=1536&bih=730&dpr=1.25,0,0,,,,,,True,,,"[""event_236_22aa3070-f2ff-4eb3-a755-44e08e46d14c_00000.jpg"", ""event_236_22aa3070-f2ff-4eb3-a755-44e08e46d14c_00001.jpg""]",,