346,BristolRoom,,2026-02-07,,112 rue du Faubourg Saint Honoré,Paris,,,,,,,,,,,"At the heart of Le Bristol Paris, the Imperial Suite is reimagined through the brushstrokes of George Condo. A true collector’s apartment, this 320 m² space blends the timeless elegance of French craftsmanship with the boldness of American pop art. Unique paintings, bespoke furniture, and exceptional pieces by Giacometti and Cocteau compose a setting where every detail tells a story. An intimate and luxurious artistic retreat, where art is not only admired but fully experienced.",,,,,,0,,,,75008,Île-de-France,,True,False,100.0,,,,,,,100.0€,,,,,10000000,,,,,,https://www.le-voyage.com/fr/hotels-de-luxe/hotel-le-bristol-paris-22/chambres/imperial-suite-3681,116,,,1,"🇫🇷 Au cœur du Bristol Paris, la Suite Impériale se réinvente sous le pinceau de George Condo. Véritable appartement de collectionneur, cet espace de 320 m² mêle l’élégance intemporelle de l’artisanat français à l’audace du pop art américain. Toiles inédites, mobilier sur-mesure et pièces d’exception signées Giacometti ou Cocteau composent un décor où chaque détail raconte une histoire. Un refuge artistique, intime et luxueux, où l’art ne se contemple pas seulement, mais se vit pleinement. 🇬🇧 At the heart of Le Bristol Paris, the Imperial Suite is reimagined through the brushstrokes of George Condo. A True collector’s apartment, this 320 m² space blends the timeless elegance of French craftsmanship with the boldness of American pop art. Unique paintings, bespoke furniture, and exceptional pieces by Giacometti and Cocteau create a setting where every detail tells a story. An intimate and luxurious artistic retreat where art is not only admired but truly lived. #LeBristolParis #SuiteImperiale #OetkerCollection #GeorgeCondo #ArtAndLuxury #ParisLuxury",,,https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=481f0124cb8ccb74&rlz=1C1GCEA_frFR1162FR1162&hl=fr-FR&sxsrf=AE3TifNOj_JvYTpi25y3tUoKS5BBUbPXNg:1756157310367&uds=AOm0WdE2fekQnsyfYEw8JPYozOKzOPZzX