303,BringCafe,,2025-08-23,,240 Rue Léon Gambetta,Lille,,,,,,,,,,,"𝙱𝚁𝙸𝙽𝙶 𝙲𝙰𝙵𝙴́• ☕️💕 We found the most girly and Instagrammable brunch spot in 𝙻𝙸𝙻𝙻𝙴 📍💋 The place is absolutely gorgeous 😱 There are incredible photo spots for guaranteed quality content 📸🌸

