512,Bomb squad,,2025-08-29,0,5 Rue Servient,Lyon,Rhône,France,0,125,False,True,False,False,False,False,"Take on the challenge and try to defuse the bomb to join the Bomb Squad and save the world.

1 hour of next-generation adventure in a space of over 70 m².

