319,Méert,,2025-08-23,,25-27 Rue Esquermoise,Lille,,,,,,,,,,,"🍫 Méert – Lille’s gourmet institution since 1761.
Famous for its Madagascar vanilla-filled waffles, Maison Méert embodies the excellence of French pastry and chocolate craftsmanship. With its elegant tearoom, refined creations, and centuries-old heritage, every visit is an invitation to indulgence and the French art of living. ✨🥐",,,,,,0,3.0620654,50.6377575,,59000,Hauts-de-France,,True,False,27.0,,,,,,,27.0€,,,,,10000000,,,,,,https://www.meert.fr/fr/,116,,,0,"🍫 Méert – L’institution gourmande de Lille depuis 1761.
