367,Jablines,,2026-02-07,,Jablines-Annet,Paris,,,,,,,,,,,"🌞 Jablines-Annet – The largest leisure park in the Paris region.
Just 40 minutes from Paris, enjoy a huge natural area around a lake: sandy beach, supervised swimming, water sports (sailing, kayaking, paddleboarding), horse riding, cycling, and kids’ playgrounds. Perfect for a family day out or fun with friends. 🚣‍♂️🏖️",,,,,1,0,2.7340414,48.9130014,,77450,Île-de-France,,True,True,12.0,12.0,,,,,,12.0€ / 12.0€ réduit,,,,,10000000,,,,,,https://jablines-annet.iledeloisirs.fr/,116,,,1,"🌞 Jablines-Annet – La grande base de loisirs d’Île-de-France.
